parameters: \C[3]Spyria\C[0]. A land on the brink of chaos. Nations vie for control of the world..\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^
Their battles leave only charred husks of what used to be great centers of commerce and humanity..\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^

However, no one knows the true dangers that lay awaiting them.  A thousand years has passed since the world was cast into darkness, and memories are short...\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\|\|\|\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^
But there are those who would re-awaken the ancient powers, and seek to harness them to bring the world to its knees.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\|\|\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^
Could anyone truly be foolish enough to repeat the terrible mistakes of old?\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\|\|\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^
In Northern \C[3]Spyria\C[0], a remote corner of the world removed from war, our story begins with a most unlikely hero...\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\|\|\|\|\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\.\^
